I think a lift would be more cost effective and useful.  There are lifts
as cheap as $1800 - you probably ca't do a proper pit for that, and you can't
take your drivetrain and suspenion out with a pit.  I'm researching lift
options right now for the 2nd garage I want to build.

Just my .02

